{"tid":1087524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"動物園猩猩真係人扮！","createTime":"2019-04-01T11:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T12:29:51.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"16524ce396c21fa309e77db83084368718e8d105","tid":1087524,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190401/640_a596bcbd1aa058e25b989a9aca2be4ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190401%2F640_a596bcbd1aa058e25b989a9aca2be4ee.jpg&h=ba914c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n動物園裡的動物如果出現類似人類的舉動時，網友們常會開玩笑說其實是工讀生假扮的，結果中國江蘇省常州市淹城野生動物世界來真的，安排了2名工作人員穿上猩猩服裝冒充猩猩，引發遊客不滿，動物園趕緊澄清，<span style=\"color: red;\">其實是愚人節活動。</span><br />\n<br />\n有中國遊客帶小孩到動物園，結果發現猩猩竟然人類假扮，氣得在網上發文痛批「沒想到偌大的場館，一隻猩猩都沒有，只有兩個人穿著廉價的道具服上躥下跳，我花180是為了來看這個的？！」不滿動物園的荒唐行為讓小孩失望，呼籲官方介入整頓。<br />\n<br />\n動物園得知引發誤會後發文澄清，表示這其實是園方推出的愚人節「真假動物」活動，是希望透過這種無傷大雅的小活動，來豐富遊客的遊玩體驗，坦承並未事先公告，但強調所有動物都正常外放。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190401/640_26965013a7ebf9762f07d68e21e33e30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190401%2F640_26965013a7ebf9762f07d68e21e33e30.jpg&h=069ac980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190401/1543611/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190401%2F1543611%2F&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQiwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=d694bfc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190401%2F1543611%2F&h=3ebe34c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190401/1543611/</a>"},{"pid":"df09d9aa4fe3fe53bc505aa2e2d97f454fdafd21","tid":1087524,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c82e16f1fe506162c83338c89cfd9679ae88e8","tid":1087524,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"日日都愚人節<br />\n反正支那最多"},{"pid":"26e5724ff8ba89e6d27a5e5cc32cd00d1978fc0f","tid":1087524,"uid":141763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"支那有野真架咩？<br />\n咁佢地味日日都係愚人節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f7d9d0804c5e6d1159ad5d8bb24b3f3efc890a","tid":1087524,"uid":2994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7082cd004322703b4ff06fade62e9661116db569","tid":1087524,"uid":38345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:04:07.000Z","msg":"10月1日都係愚人節"},{"pid":"63b68d367b2313027d614b5dbc2f6bec43b9513d","tid":1087524,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:25:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/hit/daily/article/20130815/18379053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fhit%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130815%2F18379053&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQiwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=f4fd6b04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fhit%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130815%2F18379053&h=2503830a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/hit/daily/article/20130815/18379053</a><br />\n藏獒當獅子都試過啦"},{"pid":"92a4545fe33e07391135db72b031eba9db43c1f7","tid":1087524,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:29:51.000Z","msg":"Deadpool 生毛?"}]}